    "description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2325390/extras/67507e5526e26698e34be3053d8ac6a6.avif?t=1763461611\" width=400 height=388 /></span><br><br><strong>游戏剧情</strong><br>在这个衰退的未来世界里，<br>残存的人们靠挖掘遗迹资源生存，<br>随着时间的推移，形成了一个新的职业——天空机士。<br>机士们驾驶飞船在荒废的世界中航行，专门探索充满危险的遗迹并进行战斗。<br><br>游戏的故事从主角，金发少女机士多洛塔，<br>某一天在的遗迹战斗中意外发现一名失忆的女孩阿佳塔。<br>阿佳塔来自于已消逝的遗迹文明，她的出现与遗迹内部的机器人突然活化有着某种连结。<br>这也引起了空贼的注意，展开了激烈的战斗。<br>机士协会的伙伴们，莉塔，红，贝儿相继来帮忙。<br><br>游戏有着丰富的关卡与刺激的战斗，<br>许多关卡也会有伙伴一起战斗！<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2325390/extras/14546dde1eeef413926315d995f7251b.poster.avif?t=1763461611\" width=656 height=368 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2325390/extras/14546dde1eeef413926315d995f7251b.webm?t=1763461611\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2325390/extras/14546dde1eeef413926315d995f7251b.mp4?t=1763461611\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>游戏玩法</strong><br>游戏为横向卷轴动作游戏，<br>在不同的关卡有不同的玩法，<br>除了主角多洛塔本身外，<br>还有多个伙伴会一起战斗，<br>与各式各样的伙伴一起攻克各种关卡！<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2325390/extras/803f830f4bc949da4fe818759e6fb96a.poster.avif?t=1763461611\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2325390/extras/803f830f4bc949da4fe818759e6fb96a.webm?t=1763461611\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2325390/extras/803f830f4bc949da4fe818759e6fb96a.mp4?t=1763461611\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>◆丰富的演出与剧情对话</strong><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><vid